We have increased funding to our welfare programs, especially the community kitchen launched by Manoly in '51. The progressives are pleased, and their strength risies. [? if black_thursday_seen > 0 : In an age of economic crisis, this will be helpful for improving our standing among the workers and the unemployed. ?]



