It is not enough for the PFJP to solely be a political party. The Sordish Singer League, People's Sports, and our schools and libraries are crucial to our electoral chances. Funding these organizations may very well give us an edge in upcoming local elections.

[? if sa_strength > 500 : However, it feels frivolous to spend on sports and choirs when the fascists are murdering us in the streets. ?]


