Our youth organizations have long been vastly unorganized and decentralized - which pales in comparison with our malenyevist and nationalist counterparts. 

[? if new_youth == 0 : The "New Youth" is an awaited project of the liberals, an effort to form a cohesive and structured program for our younger sords. The so-called Young Plan is simply not cutting it anymore. We have now taken steps to officialize its creation. ?]

[? if new_youth == 2 : The New Youth is formed! This is a moment of celebration fo our party, as we are able to sway radicalized young adults away from nationalist talking points. ?]

[? if new_youth > 2 : We continue funding the New Youth, expanding the organization and attracting younger voters towards liberalism. ?]


